.19\% with an AI-assisted system, while the time requirements reduced significantly from 90 to 7.62 min on average. Accurate and objective seizure counting is an important factor in epilepsy. An AI-assisted system can help improve efficiency and accuracy alongside human experts, particularly in low and middle-income countries with limited expert human resources.},
